MARKET SIZING
  Calculate TAM:
  Identify total potential users/customers globally
  Multiply by average selling price or annual value
  Cross-check with industry reports for validation
  Narrow to SAM:
  Apply geographic constraints
  Apply demographic and psychographic filters
  Apply technological or implementation constraints
  Exclude segments you explicitly won't serve
  Project realistic SOM:
  Analyze competitive landscape and existing market shares
  Consider your distribution reach and marketing budget
  Apply realistic conversion rates
  Project year-by-year growth based on resources and capacity
  

